      <hedline>
        <hl1>Malakhov Out 6 Weeks</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Vladimir Malakhov of Montreal Canadiens will miss six weeks of play because of broken thumb (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Montreal Canadiens said defenseman VLADIMIR MALAKHOV would be out at least six weeks after breaking his right thumb during a fight in Monday's 6-0 loss to the Ottawa Senators. Malakhov is Montreal's top-scoring defenseman this season with 3 goals and 15 assists.</p>
        <p>(Bloomberg)</p>
      </block>
